result.name: Bafang Dumplings

reviews.text: Good dumplings - my local friend liked them.
This place is affordable and delicious.
Great dumplings from Taiwan at very reasonable price and of good quality!

Highly recommend!! Food quality beyond expectation. Taiwanese beef noodle is the best, also dumpling and black pearl milk tea which is not too sweet. 
I will come back next time for sure.

On Lantau Island, close to the Meteo Station, this is a kiosk located in a mall. Service is barely existing, you order at the counter and a server bring your dishes.  We had veggies spring rolls, pork dumplings, 1 coke and 1 iced jasmine tea. They don't accept cards, only cash but, for an 80 HKD bill, we went to withdraw at an atm on the 1 floor.
